{"word":"Bow","slug":"bow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bow</b> 1. A weapon<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=16'>Gen 21:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=20'>Gen 21:20</a> <br/> - Made of brass<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=35'>2Sa 22:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=20&verse=24'>Job 20:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=18&verse=34'>Psa 18:34</a> <br/> - Made of wood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=39&verse=9'>Eze 39:9</a> <br/> - Used in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=13&verse=18'>Isa 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=4'>Lam 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=39&verse=3'>Eze 39:3</a> <br/> - Used by the Elamites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=35'>Jer 49:35</a> <br/> - David instructed the Israelites in the use of, by writing war song to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=18'>2Sa 1:18</a> <br/> - Used in hunting<br/> <a href='S:Archery'>Archery</a>; <a href='S:Arrow'>Arrow</a> <br/> - Figurative<br/> <a href='S:Archery'>Archery</a>; <a href='S:Arrow'>Arrow</a> <br/> - Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=24'>Gen 49:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=16&verse=13'>Job 16:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=29&verse=20'>Job 29:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=57'>Psa 78:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=3&verse=12'>Lam 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=5'>Hos 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofg